The Smokefree Partnership is a private Foundation.&#xd;
It has 5 Main partners:&#xd;
* Cancer Research UK (CRUK),&#xd;
* European Heart Network (EHN),&#xd;
* Dutch Cancer Society (DCS)&#xd;
* Norwegian Cancer Society (NCS)&#xd;
* Belgian Foundation against Cancer (BFaC)&#xd;
&#xd;
It also has around 40 partners in the SFP Coalition (listed  http://www.smokefreepartnership.eu/sfp-coalition-partners)
